Class Paper

  • java.lang.Object
    • pr3k.model.Paper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Paper
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class holds the info needed for a paper object. This class is immutable and has been made final to prevent sub classing.
    Version:
    October 2013
    Author:
    Cody Shafer
